    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its ownership. The exterior is clean with only a few minor stone chips and light surface scratches consistent with regular use, while the interior remains in great shape with no tears in the upholstery and all electronics functioning as they should. Mechanically, the car is solid, providing a smooth ride and reliable performance for its next owner. It\u2019s a great choice for someone looking for a dependable, quality vehicle that still looks and drives very well.",
