      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a dependable daily driver for someone who values utility over aesthetics. While the engine and transmission are in good working order and the car runs reliably, there are visible signs of age including minor exterior dings, some paint fading, and noticeable wear on the interior upholstery. All major systems are functional, though it lacks the polish of a newer model. It has been recently serviced and is ready for the road, offering a solid mechanical foundation for a budget-conscious buyer.",
