      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. This example has undergone critical preventative maintenance, including professional rear subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive Double-VANOS overhaul to ensure precise variable valve timing. The 6-speed manual transmission shifts crisply, sending power to the rear wheels through a variable M-differential lock. The suspension geometry remains tight with updated bushings, providing the communicative feedback expected from this iconic chassis. While showing signs of honest use, the mechanical vitals are robust, making it an ideal candidate for an enthusiast seeking a visceral, analog performance machine.",
      "price": 34500.0,
