    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle strikes the perfect balance between luxury and everyday utility. The exterior retains a deep, glossy shine, though a few minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small scuff on the rear passenger wheel reflect its honest road history. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary; the premium upholstery is supple with only light creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster, and every electronic feature\u2014from the intuitive infotainment system to the dual-zone climate control\u2014operates flawlessly. Under the hood, the engine runs smooth and quiet, benefiting from a documented history of synthetic oil changes and scheduled inspections. Recent preventative maintenance includes a fresh set of high-performance all-season tires and a new battery. It shifts crisply through all gears and handles the road with the confidence of a much newer car. Non-smoker owned, garage-kept, and sold with a complete set of service records. This is a reliable, turn-key vehicle ready for its next chapter.",
